name: I'm Shxka
description:
Hello everyone, I'm Shxka 🙏

Nice to meet you. Let me introduce myself briefly.

I am 22 now I live in Chiang Mai, Thailand.

Now I've been out of my full-time job at the company for a full month.
With the goal of learning about psychology, spirituality, science, energy, religious knowledge, healing, healing, helping people of different abilities, languages, communication, traveling around the world.

and self-development to lead a wonderful life by doing what you want without worrying. (Must not cause trouble for others) Live simply, be happy and peaceful each day, live truly, appreciate what you have.

Finally, I wish everyone to live a peaceful and peaceful life each day, being as conscious as they truly love themselves.

Thank you for your support 🤍
